::Firaxis::
       He floats down to stand in front of Rodimus.  His slight but imposing 
form standing tall.  "I am evicting you on the authority of those living here 
and those who wish to preserve life here.  You may no longer use this planet 
as your battlefield.  GET OUT!"

--part1_159.17988fa8.2b0868ae_boundary
